cu.explanation_en: Setting GNB_IPV4_ADDRESS_FOR_NG_AMF to an invalid IP address '999.999.999.999' will cause AMF connection failures and NG interface establishment issues.

du.explanation_en: Setting physCellId to 1008 (exceeding valid range 0-1007) will cause invalid physical cell identification and synchronization failures.
du.explanation_zh: 將 physCellId 設定為 1008（超出有效範圍 0-1007）會導致無效的物理小區識別和同步失敗。
